landwirtschaftliche rentenbank
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Government
Industry: Government Development Banks
Sub-Industry: -
Landwirtschaftliche Rentenbank operates as a public law institution. The Bank provides refinancing for all types of projects associated with agriculture and rural areas within the European Union. Landwirtschaftliche operates under the legal supervision of the German federal government and the banking supervision of the federal financial supervisory agency.




