Credit Rating is an opinion of a credit rating agency about credit worthiness of a company 
		or a government. Landwirtschaftliche Rentenbank is rated by Fitch and Moody's.
Credit ratings assigned to Landwirtschaftliche Rentenbank as of April 2016 are shown in details in the following sections.
FitchLong-term issuer default rating is Fitch's view of a credit institution's relative vulnerability 
		to default on its financial obligations, for Landwirtschaftliche Rentenbank it is set to AAA  (highest credit quality), outlook is stable  (not likely to change). The rating is not on watch. Short-term issuer default rating for Landwirtschaftliche Rentenbank is set to F1+  (highest short-term credit quality).
