Viability rating for Landwirtschaftliche Rentenbank is not set support rating is 1  (extremely high probability of external support); support rating floor is AAA  (highest credit quality). 
Moody'sLong-term rating for Landwirtschaftliche Rentenbank it is set to Aaa  (prime). Long-term bank deposit rating is Aaa  (prime). Bank financial strength rating is not set. Short-term rating is not assigned. 

